bilingual.source: The painting turned out to be a fake.
Can you distinguish which one is fake?
bilingual.target: 你能辨别出哪一个是假的吗？

bilingual.source: He used a fake ID to get into the club.
bilingual.target: 他用假的身份证进入了俱乐部。

bilingual.source: The company was caught selling fake products.
bilingual.target: 这家公司被抓到在卖假的产品。

bilingual.source: Don't let anyone diddle you with fake promises.
bilingual.target: 不要让任何人用虚假的承诺欺骗你。

bilingual.source: She gave a fake smile to hide her true feelings.
bilingual.target: 她给了一个假的微笑来掩饰她的真实感受。

bilingual.source: He made a fake excuse to leave the meeting early.
bilingual.target: 他编了一个假的借口提前离开了会议。

bilingual.source: The investors were defrauded by a fake investment scheme.
bilingual.target: 投资者被一个虚假的投资计划欺诈了。

bilingual.source: The con artist tried to entrap the victim with a fake investment scheme.
bilingual.target: 骗子试图用一个虚假的投资计划来诱捕受害者。
对虚假的钻石金子或银子都没有感觉了

list.abstract: 《绝爱追缉令》（FAKE）是日本漫画家真东砂波的代表作，单行本共7卷，由青磁出版社出版，是90年代初期开始连载的漫画。 该作以两位主角与大毒枭集团搏斗为主线，其中含有不同类型的刑事案件。故事围绕两位警察之间的情感展开，讲述了日裔查探警员（Ryo）与拍档（Dee）在共同处理案件的过程中产生了一段朦胧爱情的故事。 另有同名动画《绝爱追缉令》于1998年4月21日在日本上映。
fake是一个英语单词，意思是伪造的。

yingyinNormal.en: Cause you know that's all fake. It's all done on a computer? It's like that video, what is it?
yingyinNormal.zh: 这些可都是假的，是电脑特效，就像那个视频一样，什么来着？

yingyinNormal.en: Look at these authentic fake medals. I tell you, mom's gonna be voted best dressed at the make-believe military academy.
yingyinNormal.zh: 瞧瞧这些假徽章，妈会得到“最佳服装奖”在假的军校里。

yingyinNormal.en: It's all a fugazi. You know what a fugazi is? Uh. Fugayzi. It's a fake. Fugayzi, fugazi, it's a whazy, it's a woozy, it's...
yingyinNormal.zh: 这都是忽悠人的，你知道什么是忽悠吧，忽悠，就是假的。忽悠来，忽悠去。

yingyinNormal.en: We had one of those silly fake weddings.
yingyinNormal.zh: 办了那种傻傻的假婚礼。

yingyinNormal.en: Gotta be a pretty good fake to fool Glasses.
yingyinNormal.zh: 能骗过眼镜儿，肯定够逼真啊。

yingyinNormal.en: You'll have to fake it. Lady Mary, Edith, Mr Branson...
yingyinNormal.zh: 你们只能装装了，玛丽小姐，伊迪丝，布兰森先生…

yingyinNormal.en: Max, you do fake stairs so well. I know. It's the second best thing I fake.
yingyinNormal.zh: 麦克斯，你好会演假装下楼梯。我知道，这是我"假"得第二好的事。

yingyinNormal.en: I'm just saying, if we fake got back together, that's totally not how it fake happened.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我只是想说，如果我们假装和好，那也肯定不是这么和好的。

yingyinNormal.en: I don't believe this. You got him to pretend he was some fake doctor? Fake? Excuse me? Hello?
yingyinNormal.zh: 我不敢相信，你要他假扮医生？假扮？对不起，喂。

yingyinNormal.en: Hey, Mr. Phillips. Nice suit. Right there. That was so fake!
yingyinNormal.zh: 嘿，菲利浦先生，很好看的西装。抓到了，真是好假！

yingyinNormal.en: Nikita doesn't have time to fake that. There's too much heat.
yingyinNormal.zh: 尼基塔没时间伪造这种文件。风声太紧了

yingyinNormal.en: But when I'd ask him where they were, he'd give me a fake address.
yingyinNormal.zh: 可每次我问他派对在哪里，他都会给我假地址。

yingyinNormal.en: Then she moved to England and she picked up this fake British accent.
yingyinNormal.zh: 后来她搬去英国了，还学了假惺惺的英国口音。

yingyinNormal.en: Now you think I wouldn't enjoy that, because it is so fake, but I still do.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你以为你说得太假，我会不相信，但我还是觉得很高兴。

yingyinNormal.en: I didn't care if they were real or fake. It was a great way to pass the time.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我不在乎故事的真假，这是个消磨时光的好办法。

yingyinNormal.en: The Internet. She gets a fake ID, she sends money to herself. What does this mean?
yingyinNormal.zh: 网络。她制造假身份，给自己汇钱。这是什么意思？

yingyinNormal.en: You were just being so nice to him. I was faking it. Can't you tell when I'm being fake?
yingyinNormal.zh: 你看起来跟他很好啊。我是装出来的，你难道看不出来我是装的吗？

yingyinNormal.en: Maybe. Or maybe hiding behind a fake screenname gives the people the courage to go negative.
yingyinNormal.zh: 也许吧，又或者藏在网名的假面之后让人有勇气去攻击别人。

yingyinNormal.en: I'm not gonna make a fake appointment with a psychiatrist. What would I say is wrong with me?
yingyinNormal.zh: 我才不要假装病人去看精神科医生，我要假装有啥毛病呢？

yingyinNormal.en: This is so exciting. Soon, my upper lip will be the same fake blonde as my beautiful best friend.
yingyinNormal.zh: 好兴奋哦，我唇上的汗毛很快会跟我美丽好友一样有着好看的假金色了。

direction_info.description:
数据源自2012-2023年12年间全国考研试卷，由搜狗翻译进行大数据分析汇总，数据仅供参考。

<highlight> 考频分布</highlight>
由搜狗翻译收集历年真题试卷、汇总单词出现的总频次、释义分布。题型选自2012-2023年全国考研英语一和考研英语二共24套考研试卷，包括阅读、完型填空、翻译、写作等所有题型。

<highlight> 考纲释义</highlight>
精选全国考研考纲词汇、单词义项，由搜狗大数据与考纲、历年真题进行匹配。

<highlight>真题例句</highlight>
精选2012-2023年12年间全国考研英语一和考研英语二试卷，由搜狗大数据与搜索内容匹配历年真题例句。

搜狗翻译拥有最终解释权。

sense_info_list.en: not genuine or real; being an imitation of the genuine article
sense_info_list.zh: 假的; 伪造的(物品); 伪造

examination_example.sentence: But don't overdo it or be <highlight>fake</highlight> about it.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 但不要做得太过，也不要假装。

examination_example.sentence: The Barna survey found that a main cause for the <highlight>fake</highlight> news problem is readers' misinterpretation.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 巴纳调查发现，假新闻问题的一个主要原因是读者的误解。

examination_example.sentence: About a third say the problem of <highlight>fake</highlight> news lies in "misinterpretation or exaggeration of actual news" via social media.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 约三分之一的人表示，假新闻的问题在于通过社交媒体“曲解或夸大真实新闻”。

word_usage.usage: fake既可作及物动词又可作不及物动词。作及物动词时，其后可以接名词或者代词，如：He faked the results. 他伪造了结果。

examination_example.sentence: <highlight>Fake</highlight> news websites often use addresses that sound like real newspapers, but don't have many real stories about other topics.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 假新闻网站经常使用听起来像真正报纸的地址，但没有很多关于其他话题的真实故事。

examination_example.sentence: If you do find it on many other sites, then it probably isn't <highlight>fake</highlight> (although there are some exceptions).
examination_example.sentence_trans: 如果你在许多其他网站上找到它，那么它可能不是假的(尽管也有一些例外)。

examination_example.sentence: If you find a news story that you know is <highlight>fake</highlight>, the most important advice is: don't share it!
examination_example.sentence_trans: 如果你发现一个你知道是假的新闻，最重要的建议是:不要分享它!
